text.section:
A waterfowl processing operation shall keep on forms provided by the Department a record of:
The number of each species of wild waterfowl processed, received by, or in the custody of the operation;
The location (county and state) where each wild waterfowl received by the operation was taken;
The date each wild waterfowl was received by the operation;
The name and address of the person from whom each wild waterfowl was received;
The date each wild waterfowl was disposed of by the operation; and
The name and address of the person to whom each wild waterfowl was delivered.
